breakingChangesNotes: To provide more comprehensive threat protection and align with current PAN-OS the `pan-os-hygiene-check-url-filtering-profiles` command has been updated to check an extended best-practice list of URL categories to block: abused-drugs, adult, command-and-control, compromised-websites, gambling, grayware, hacking, malware, phishing, questionable, ransomware, scanning-activity, weapons
